{"id":245,"ayahs":[{"number":79,"arabic":"قَالَ مَعَاذَ ٱللَّهِ أَن نَّأْخُذَ إِلَّا مَن وَجَدْنَا مَتَٰعَنَا عِندَهُۥٓ إِنَّآ إِذًۭا لَّظَٰلِمُونَ","translation":"He answered: \"May God preserve us from [the sin of] detaining any other than him with whom we have found our property-for then, behold, we would indeed be evildoers!\"","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/1675.mp3","surahId":12,"words":[{"id":63810,"position":1,"arabic":"قَالَ","translation":"সে বললো","audioUrl":"wbw/012_079_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":63811,"position":2,"arabic":"مَعَاذَ","translation":"\"আশ্রয়","audioUrl":"wbw/012_079_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":63812,"position":3,"arabic":"ٱللَّهِ","translation":"\"আল্লাহ্‌র","audioUrl":"wbw/012_079_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":63813,"position":4,"arabic":"أَن","translation":"যে","audioUrl":"wbw/012_079_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":63814,"position":5,"arabic":"نَّأْخُذَ","translation":"ধরবো আমরা","audioUrl":"wbw/012_079_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":63815,"position":6,"arabic":"إِلَّا","translation":"ছাড়া","audioUrl":"wbw/012_079_006.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":63816,"position":7,"arabic":"مَن","translation":"যাকে","audioUrl":"wbw/012_079_007.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":63817,"position":8,"arabic":"وَجَدْنَا","translation":"আমরা পেয়েছি","audioUrl":"wbw/012_079_008.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":63818,"position":9,"arabic":"مَتَـٰعَنَا","translation":"আমাদের সামগ্রী","audioUrl":"wbw/012_079_009.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":63819,"position":10,"arabic":"عِندَهُۥٓ","translation":"তার কাছে","audioUrl":"wbw/012_079_010.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":63820,"position":11,"arabic":"إِنَّآ","translation":"নিশ্চয়ই আমরা","audioUrl":"wbw/012_079_011.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":63821,"position":12,"arabic":"إِذًۭا","translation":"তখন (হবো)","audioUrl":"wbw/012_079_012.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":63822,"position":13,"arabic":"لَّظَـٰلِمُونَ","translation":"অবশ্যই সীমালঙ্ঘনকারীদের (অন্তর্ভুক্ত)\"","audioUrl":"wbw/012_079_013.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":63823,"position":14,"arabic":"٧٩","translation":"(৭৯)","audioUrl":null,"charTypeName":"end"}]},{"number":80,"arabic":"فَلَمَّا ٱسْتَيْـَٔسُوا۟ مِنْهُ خَلَصُوا۟ نَجِيًّۭا ۖ قَالَ كَبِيرُهُمْ أَلَمْ تَعْلَمُوٓا۟ أَنَّ أَبَاكُمْ قَدْ أَخَذَ عَلَيْكُم مَّوْثِقًۭا مِّنَ ٱللَّهِ وَمِن قَبْلُ مَا فَرَّطتُمْ فِى يُوسُفَ ۖ فَلَنْ أَبْرَحَ ٱلْأَرْضَ حَتَّىٰ يَأْذَنَ لِىٓ أَبِىٓ أَوْ يَحْكُمَ ٱللَّهُ لِى ۖ وَهُوَ خَيْرُ ٱلْحَٰكِمِينَ","translation":"And so, when they lost all hope of [moving] him, they withdrew to take counsel [among themselves]. The eldest of them said: \"Do you not remember that your father has bound you by a solemn pledge before God - and how, before that, you had failed with regard to Joseph? Hence, I shall not depart from this land till my father gives me leave or God passes judgment in my favour: for He is the best of all judges.","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/1676.mp3","surahId":12,"words":[{"id":64107,"position":1,"arabic":"فَلَمَّا","translation":"অতঃপর যখন","audioUrl":"wbw/012_080_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":64108,"position":2,"arabic":"ٱسْتَيْـَٔسُوا۟","translation":"তারা নিরাশ হলো","audioUrl":"wbw/012_080_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":64109,"position":3,"arabic":"مِنْهُ","translation":"তার থেকে","audioUrl":"wbw/012_080_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":64110,"position":4,"arabic":"خَلَصُوا۟","translation":"নির্জনে গিয়ে বসলো","audioUrl":"wbw/012_080_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":64111,"position":5,"arabic":"نَجِيًّۭا ۖ","translation":"পরামর্শে","audioUrl":"wbw/012_080_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":64113,"position":6,"arabic":"قَالَ","translation":"বললো","audioUrl":"wbw/012_080_007.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":64114,"position":7,"arabic":"كَبِيرُهُمْ","translation":"তাদের বড়জন","audioUrl":"wbw/012_080_008.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":64115,"position":8,"arabic":"أَلَمْ","translation":"\"না কি","audioUrl":"wbw/012_080_009.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":64116,"position":9,"arabic":"تَعْلَمُوٓا۟","translation":"তোমরা জেনেছো","audioUrl":"wbw/012_080_010.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":64117,"position":10,"arabic":"أَنَّ","translation":"যে","audioUrl":"wbw/012_080_011.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":64118,"position":11,"arabic":"أَبَاكُمْ","translation":"তোমাদের পিতা","audioUrl":"wbw/012_080_012.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":64119,"position":12,"arabic":"قَدْ","translation":"নিশ্চয়ই","audioUrl":"wbw/012_080_013.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":64120,"position":13,"arabic":"أَخَذَ","translation":"নিয়েছেন","audioUrl":"wbw/012_080_014.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":64121,"position":14,"arabic":"عَلَيْكُم","translation":"তোমাদের হ'তে","audioUrl":"wbw/012_080_015.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":64122,"position":15,"arabic":"مَّوْثِقًۭا","translation":"প্রতিশ্রুতি","audioUrl":"wbw/012_080_016.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":64123,"position":16,"arabic":"مِّنَ","translation":"নামে","audioUrl":"wbw/012_080_017.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":64124,"position":17,"arabic":"ٱللَّهِ","translation":"আল্লাহর","audioUrl":"wbw/012_080_018.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":64125,"position":18,"arabic":"وَمِن","translation":"এবং থেকেই","audioUrl":"wbw/012_080_019.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":64126,"position":19,"arabic":"قَبْلُ","translation":"পূর্ব","audioUrl":"wbw/012_080_020.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":64127,"position":20,"arabic":"مَا","translation":"কি","audioUrl":"wbw/012_080_021.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":64128,"position":21,"arabic":"فَرَّطتُمْ","translation":"তোমরা অন্যায় করেছো","audioUrl":"wbw/012_080_022.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":64129,"position":22,"arabic":"فِى","translation":"ব্যাপারে","audioUrl":"wbw/012_080_023.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":64130,"position":23,"arabic":"يُوسُفَ ۖ","translation":"ইউসুফের","audioUrl":"wbw/012_080_024.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":64132,"position":24,"arabic":"فَلَنْ","translation":"অতএব কখনও না","audioUrl":"wbw/012_080_026.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":64133,"position":25,"arabic":"أَبْرَحَ","translation":"ছেড়ে যাবো আমি","audioUrl":"wbw/012_080_027.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":64134,"position":26,"arabic":"ٱلْأَرْضَ","translation":"এ দেশ","audioUrl":"wbw/012_080_028.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":64135,"position":27,"arabic":"حَتَّىٰ","translation":"যতক্ষণ না","audioUrl":"wbw/012_080_029.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":64136,"position":28,"arabic":"يَأْذَنَ","translation":"অনুমতি দিবেন","audioUrl":"wbw/012_080_030.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":64137,"position":29,"arabic":"لِىٓ","translation":"আমাকে","audioUrl":"wbw/012_080_031.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":64138,"position":30,"arabic":"أَبِىٓ","translation":"আমার পিতা","audioUrl":"wbw/012_080_032.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":64139,"position":31,"arabic":"أَوْ","translation":"বা","audioUrl":"wbw/012_080_033.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":64140,"position":32,"arabic":"يَحْكُمَ","translation":"মীমাংসা করবেন","audioUrl":"wbw/012_080_034.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":64141,"position":33,"arabic":"ٱللَّهُ","translation":"আল্লাহ","audioUrl":"wbw/012_080_035.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":64142,"position":34,"arabic":"لِى ۖ","translation":"আমার জন্যে (অন্য কিছু)","audioUrl":"wbw/012_080_036.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":64144,"position":35,"arabic":"وَهُوَ","translation":"এবং তিনিই","audioUrl":"wbw/012_080_038.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":64145,"position":36,"arabic":"خَيْرُ","translation":"শ্রেষ্ঠ","audioUrl":"wbw/012_080_039.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":64146,"position":37,"arabic":"ٱلْحَـٰكِمِينَ","translation":"বিচারকদের","audioUrl":"wbw/012_080_040.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":64147,"position":38,"arabic":"٨٠","translation":"(৮০)","audioUrl":null,"charTypeName":"end"}]},{"number":81,"arabic":"ٱرْجِعُوٓا۟ إِلَىٰٓ أَبِيكُمْ فَقُولُوا۟ يَٰٓأَبَانَآ إِنَّ ٱبْنَكَ سَرَقَ وَمَا شَهِدْنَآ إِلَّا بِمَا عَلِمْنَا وَمَا كُنَّا لِلْغَيْبِ حَٰفِظِينَ","translation":"[And as for you others,] return to your father and say: `O our father! Behold, thy son has stolen-but we [can] bear witness to no more than what has become known to us; and [although we gave you our pledge,] we could not guard against something that [lay hidden in the future and, hence,] was beyond the reach of our perception.","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/1677.mp3","surahId":12,"words":[{"id":64550,"position":1,"arabic":"ٱرْجِعُوٓا۟","translation":"তোমরা ফিরে যাও","audioUrl":"wbw/012_081_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":64551,"position":2,"arabic":"إِلَىٰٓ","translation":"কাছে","audioUrl":"wbw/012_081_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":64552,"position":3,"arabic":"أَبِيكُمْ","translation":"তোমাদের পিতার","audioUrl":"wbw/012_081_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":64553,"position":4,"arabic":"فَقُولُوا۟","translation":"অতঃপর তোমরা বলো","audioUrl":"wbw/012_081_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":64554,"position":5,"arabic":"يَـٰٓأَبَانَآ","translation":"হে আমাদের পিতা","audioUrl":"wbw/012_081_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":64555,"position":6,"arabic":"إِنَّ","translation":"নিশ্চয়ই","audioUrl":"wbw/012_081_006.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":64556,"position":7,"arabic":"ٱبْنَكَ","translation":"আপনার ছেলে","audioUrl":"wbw/012_081_007.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":64557,"position":8,"arabic":"سَرَقَ","translation":"চুরি করেছে","audioUrl":"wbw/012_081_008.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":64558,"position":9,"arabic":"وَمَا","translation":"এবং না","audioUrl":"wbw/012_081_009.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":64559,"position":10,"arabic":"شَهِدْنَآ","translation":"আমরা সাক্ষ্য দিচ্ছি","audioUrl":"wbw/012_081_010.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":64560,"position":11,"arabic":"إِلَّا","translation":"এ ছাড়া","audioUrl":"wbw/012_081_011.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":64561,"position":12,"arabic":"بِمَا","translation":"ঐ সম্বন্ধে যা","audioUrl":"wbw/012_081_012.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":64562,"position":13,"arabic":"عَلِمْنَا","translation":"আমরা জেনেছি","audioUrl":"wbw/012_081_013.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":64563,"position":14,"arabic":"وَمَا","translation":"এবং না","audioUrl":"wbw/012_081_014.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":64564,"position":15,"arabic":"كُنَّا","translation":"আমরা ছিলাম","audioUrl":"wbw/012_081_015.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":64565,"position":16,"arabic":"لِلْغَيْبِ","translation":"ব্যাপারে অদৃশ্যের","audioUrl":"wbw/012_081_016.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":64566,"position":17,"arabic":"حَـٰفِظِينَ","translation":"সংরক্ষক (অর্থাৎ অবহিত)","audioUrl":"wbw/012_081_017.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":64567,"position":18,"arabic":"٨١","translation":"(৮১)","audioUrl":null,"charTypeName":"end"}]},{"number":82,"arabic":"وَسْـَٔلِ ٱلْقَرْيَةَ ٱلَّتِى كُنَّا فِيهَا وَٱلْعِيرَ ٱلَّتِىٓ أَقْبَلْنَا فِيهَا ۖ وَإِنَّا لَصَٰدِقُونَ","translation":"And ask thou in the town in which we were [at the time], and of the people of the caravan with whom we travelled hither, and [thou wilt find that] we, are indeed telling the truth!\"'","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/1678.mp3","surahId":12,"words":[{"id":64964,"position":1,"arabic":"وَسْـَٔلِ","translation":"এবং জিজ্ঞেস করুন","audioUrl":"wbw/012_082_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":64965,"position":2,"arabic":"ٱلْقَرْيَةَ","translation":"জনপদের অধিবাসীদের","audioUrl":"wbw/012_082_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":64966,"position":3,"arabic":"ٱلَّتِى","translation":"যে (জনপদে)","audioUrl":"wbw/012_082_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":64967,"position":4,"arabic":"كُنَّا","translation":"আমরা ছিলাম","audioUrl":"wbw/012_082_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":64968,"position":5,"arabic":"فِيهَا","translation":"তার মধ্যে","audioUrl":"wbw/012_082_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":64969,"position":6,"arabic":"وَٱلْعِيرَ","translation":"ও যাত্রীদলকে","audioUrl":"wbw/012_082_006.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":64970,"position":7,"arabic":"ٱلَّتِىٓ","translation":"সেই (কাফেলার)","audioUrl":"wbw/012_082_007.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":64971,"position":8,"arabic":"أَقْبَلْنَا","translation":"আমরা এসেছি","audioUrl":"wbw/012_082_008.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":64972,"position":9,"arabic":"فِيهَا ۖ","translation":"যার সাথে","audioUrl":"wbw/012_082_009.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":64974,"position":10,"arabic":"وَإِنَّا","translation":"এবং নিশ্চয়ই আমরা","audioUrl":"wbw/012_082_011.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":64975,"position":11,"arabic":"لَصَـٰدِقُونَ","translation":"অবশ্যই সত্যবাদী","audioUrl":"wbw/012_082_012.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":64976,"position":12,"arabic":"٨٢","translation":"(৮২)","audioUrl":null,"charTypeName":"end"}]},{"number":83,"arabic":"قَالَ بَلْ سَوَّلَتْ لَكُمْ أَنفُسُكُمْ أَمْرًۭا ۖ فَصَبْرٌۭ جَمِيلٌ ۖ عَسَى ٱللَّهُ أَن يَأْتِيَنِى بِهِمْ جَمِيعًا ۚ إِنَّهُۥ هُوَ ٱلْعَلِيمُ ٱلْحَكِيمُ","translation":"[AND WHEN they returned to their father and told him what had happened,] he exclaimed: \"Nay, but it is your [own] minds that have made [so terrible] a happening seem a matter of little account to you! But [as for myself,] patience in adversity is most goodly; God may well bring them all [back] unto me: verily, He alone is all-knowing, truly wise!\"","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/1679.mp3","surahId":12,"words":[{"id":65264,"position":1,"arabic":"قَالَ","translation":"(ইয়াকুব) বললো","audioUrl":"wbw/012_083_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":65265,"position":2,"arabic":"بَلْ","translation":"\"বরং","audioUrl":"wbw/012_083_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":65266,"position":3,"arabic":"سَوَّلَتْ","translation":"সাজিয়ে দিয়েছে","audioUrl":"wbw/012_083_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":65267,"position":4,"arabic":"لَكُمْ","translation":"তোমাদের জন্যে","audioUrl":"wbw/012_083_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":65268,"position":5,"arabic":"أَنفُسُكُمْ","translation":"তোমাদের মন (অর্থাৎ প্রবৃত্তি)","audioUrl":"wbw/012_083_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":65269,"position":6,"arabic":"أَمْرًۭا ۖ","translation":"এ কাজ","audioUrl":"wbw/012_083_006.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":65271,"position":7,"arabic":"فَصَبْرٌۭ","translation":"অতএব ধৈর্যই","audioUrl":"wbw/012_083_008.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":65272,"position":8,"arabic":"جَمِيلٌ ۖ","translation":"উত্তম","audioUrl":"wbw/012_083_009.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":65274,"position":9,"arabic":"عَسَى","translation":"হয়তো","audioUrl":"wbw/012_083_011.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":65275,"position":10,"arabic":"ٱللَّهُ","translation":"আল্লাহ","audioUrl":"wbw/012_083_012.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":65276,"position":11,"arabic":"أَن","translation":"যে","audioUrl":"wbw/012_083_013.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":65277,"position":12,"arabic":"يَأْتِيَنِى","translation":"আমার কাছে আনবেন","audioUrl":"wbw/012_083_014.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":65278,"position":13,"arabic":"بِهِمْ","translation":"নিয়ে তাদেরকে","audioUrl":"wbw/012_083_015.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":65279,"position":14,"arabic":"جَمِيعًا ۚ","translation":"একত্রে","audioUrl":"wbw/012_083_016.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":65281,"position":15,"arabic":"إِنَّهُۥ","translation":"নিশ্চয়ই তিনি","audioUrl":"wbw/012_083_018.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":65282,"position":16,"arabic":"هُوَ","translation":"তিনিই","audioUrl":"wbw/012_083_019.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":65283,"position":17,"arabic":"ٱلْعَلِيمُ","translation":"সর্বজ্ঞ","audioUrl":"wbw/012_083_020.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":65284,"position":18,"arabic":"ٱلْحَكِيمُ","translation":"প্রজ্ঞাময়\"","audioUrl":"wbw/012_083_021.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":65285,"position":19,"arabic":"٨٣","translation":"(৮৩)","audioUrl":null,"charTypeName":"end"}]},{"number":84,"arabic":"وَتَوَلَّىٰ عَنْهُمْ وَقَالَ يَٰٓأَسَفَىٰ عَلَىٰ يُوسُفَ وَٱبْيَضَّتْ عَيْنَاهُ مِنَ ٱلْحُزْنِ فَهُوَ كَظِيمٌۭ","translation":"But he turned away from them and said: \"O woe is me for Joseph!\"-and his eyes became dim from the grief with which he was filled.","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/1680.mp3","surahId":12,"words":[{"id":65867,"position":1,"arabic":"وَتَوَلَّىٰ","translation":"এবং মুখ ফিরালো সে","audioUrl":"wbw/012_084_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":65868,"position":2,"arabic":"عَنْهُمْ","translation":"তাদের থেকে","audioUrl":"wbw/012_084_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":65869,"position":3,"arabic":"وَقَالَ","translation":"এবং বললো","audioUrl":"wbw/012_084_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":65870,"position":4,"arabic":"يَـٰٓأَسَفَىٰ","translation":"\"হায় আফসোস","audioUrl":"wbw/012_084_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":65871,"position":5,"arabic":"عَلَىٰ","translation":"জন্যে","audioUrl":"wbw/012_084_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":65872,"position":6,"arabic":"يُوسُفَ","translation":"ইউসুফের\"","audioUrl":"wbw/012_084_006.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":65873,"position":7,"arabic":"وَٱبْيَضَّتْ","translation":"এবং সাদা হয়ে গেল","audioUrl":"wbw/012_084_007.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":65874,"position":8,"arabic":"عَيْنَاهُ","translation":"তার দু'চোখ","audioUrl":"wbw/012_084_008.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":65875,"position":9,"arabic":"مِنَ","translation":"কারণে","audioUrl":"wbw/012_084_009.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":65876,"position":10,"arabic":"ٱلْحُزْنِ","translation":"শোকের","audioUrl":"wbw/012_084_010.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":65877,"position":11,"arabic":"فَهُوَ","translation":"অতঃপর সে (হয়ে গেলো)","audioUrl":"wbw/012_084_011.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":65878,"position":12,"arabic":"كَظِيمٌۭ","translation":"বিষাদপূর্ণ","audioUrl":"wbw/012_084_012.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":65879,"position":13,"arabic":"٨٤","translation":"(৮৪)","audioUrl":null,"charTypeName":"end"}]},{"number":85,"arabic":"قَالُوا۟ تَٱللَّهِ تَفْتَؤُا۟ تَذْكُرُ يُوسُفَ حَتَّىٰ تَكُونَ حَرَضًا أَوْ تَكُونَ مِنَ ٱلْهَٰلِكِينَ","translation":"Said [his sons]: \"By Go